Games::Mines
-------------
This module is the basis for mine finding game. It contains the 
basic methods necessary for a game.

It includes the basic Games::Mines module that does the game itself,
and a Games::Mines::Play module that lets you play a basic text based game.

There is also a working game, pmine, included, although it is not installed
with the rest.

Building
--------

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

